vector measure `v` on `M` to the vector measure `f ∘ v` on `N`. -/
def map_range_hom (f : M →+ N) (hf : continuous f) : vector_measure α M →+ vector_measure α N :=
{ to_fun := λ v, v.map_range f hf,
  map_zero' := map_range_zero hf,
